data.description: FHA ASSUMABLE LOAN AT 3.5%. Beautiful Plum Creek Home backing to the Plum Creek Golf Course.  This 4 bed, 4 bath home with a finished basement will be perfect for all of your needs.  Plenty of space to entertain while having the comforts of privacy and relaxation.  Main floor is equipped with updated custom family room fireplace and shelving that's pleasing to the eyes with beauty and sophistication. Kitchen is functional for all, including the chef with everything needed to prepare the most detailed meal or just a simple cup of coffee. Formal living and dining room compliment the kitchen for easy flow. Office has French doors for those who work from home or need additional space. Upstairs in its own wing, you'll find the large primary bedroom with space that includes additional sitting area and a large window with sitting cushions and pillows to admire the mountain views in the morning before your day gets started. Primary bath boasts both a separate shower, tub and a walk-in closet.  Additionally, there are 3 more bedrooms and a full bathroom.  Basement has a wet bar, comfortable great room and bathroom for the movie nights or entertaining friends.  Outside in the back is a large deck and backs to the golf course but also gives you privacy for your own personal time while enjoying the comforts of the four seasons Colorado has to offer, and you might even see some deer. This property faces south with a covered front porch, provides plenty of windows for the abundance of sunshine and for the snow melt. There is an assumable loan on this property. For more information, please contact listing agent at 303-870-2689.
